  "medusa_draft_step_tax_vs_eagle3": "Medusa 0.53 ms (one parallel head-forward) vs EAGLE-3 chain tax ~3.11 ms extra (m=3 central, #532/#295): Medusa draft is REPLACEMENT-cheaper, EAGLE-3 is MULTIPLIER-dearer",
