  "drafter_is_quality_safe_reason": "spec-dec verify is byte-exact M=8: Medusa acceptance changes ONLY E[T] (tokens/step), NOT the emitted distribution \u2014 served output == target greedy regardless of head quality. self-det/PPL invariant to the drafter, inherited from MY #523 served stack (no re-serve).",
